text: Moustafa Chellouf (born 21 March 1935) is a Tunisian former sports shooter. He competed in the 50 metre rifle, prone event at the 1960 Summer Olympics. ==References== Category:1935 births Category:Living people Category:Tunisian male sport shooters Category:Olympic shooters of Tunisia Category:Shooters at the 1960 Summer Olympics Category:People from Sfax
